{"tid":305930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好彩香港有連登咋","createTime":"2017-07-02T06:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T11:42:59.000Z","uid":23848,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a54bb57f5c88b3d53c055d281a05b4e4a6c465f","tid":305930,"uid":23848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:27:24.000Z","msg":"喺到聚埋一班&hellip;<br />\n道德撚－事事都自命正義之師，唔同意見嘅人都係狗；<br />\n封建撚 －女人唔係處的話就係雞，扑過嘢唔俾擺酒；<br />\n毒撚 － 無人約無女無朋友日日留喺屋企以為網絡就係全世界；<br />\n<br />\n呢班人都係社會潛在危險人物（但佢哋唔知），自小心靈受創（無人愛，要網上講d出位嘢擦存在感），好在有連登令佢哋可以互相安慰對方，並認同呢d不能喺正常社會生存到嘅價值觀，所以連尼住真係做咗件好大嘅善事！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5915204c1d00cf1655c431742d92c535aff9376","tid":305930,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:29:44.000Z","msg":"無所事事 一事無成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4f0d68a47390c3baacb20e7e7e482156b627e4","tid":305930,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:33:06.000Z","msg":"危險人物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf03c5961a3daf271daf9379d862e97f0906e348","tid":305930,"uid":23848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d13b0c17474702ea9b9516c35a1e7bd5986609c","tid":305930,"uid":114275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:51:43.000Z","msg":"呢樣就係要打句駁唔到啦 講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f644ccbff88fc2e0521735d19c8af899fb0be0","tid":305930,"uid":23848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:00:01.000Z","msg":"係咪講得太中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\"